OL,3,CLe Clos Mourant residents return home
OL,4,Cafter gas leak fixed
OL,6,FAround 50 homes were evacuated last
OL,7,Fnight (Saturday 14 December) due to a
OL,8,Fgas leak on Le Squez Road in Le Clos
OL,9,FMourant, St Clement.
OL,11,FThe Government moved residents to the
OL,12,FAmbassador Hotel overnight "to avoid
OL,13,Fundue anxiety ".
OL,15,FThey have now been allowed to return
OL,16,Fhome after Island Energy confirmed
OL,17,Fthis morning (Sunday 15 December),
OL,18,Fthat there have been no readings of
OL,19,Fgas in the properties for four hours.
