OL,3,CLe Clos Mourant residents return home
OL,4,Cafter gas leak fixed
OL,6,FEngineers discovered a pocket of gas
OL,7,Fin a service duct, this has since been
OL,8,Fvented and the cause of the leak fixed.
OL,10,FThey added that residual gas pockets
OL,11,Fhave been purged with clean air and no
OL,12,Flonger pose a risk.
OL,14,FSocial housing provider Andium Homes
OL,15,Fsaid their properties at Le Clos
OL,16,FMourant do not have mains gas going
OL,17,Finto them.
