OL,3,CLe Clos Mourant residents return home
OL,4,Cafter gas leak fixed
OL,6,FThe company said: "It is believed that
OL,7,Fthe leak has occurred on a nearby
OL,8,FIsland Energy gas pipe situated
OL,9,Fbeneath Le Squez Road, which passes by
OL,10,Fthe apartment block."
OL,12,F"We are already speaking to Island
OL,13,FEnergy and others to understand how
OL,14,Fgas can have been detected in that
OL,15,Farea."
OL,17,FIsland Energy apologised for the
OL,18,F"distress and inconvenience caused".
